{"tid":2176562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"BLM左膠記者同黨媒記者一起遊覽西藏做大外宣","createTime":"2020-08-27T07:27:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T11:08:03.000Z","uid":292987,"like":12,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"d1a52773d4b79e7c0eb7925706ac9626d09dd31e","tid":2176562,"uid":292987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T07:27:25.000Z","msg":"人竟然可以虛偽嘔心到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成班小粉紅同佢開心互動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌柒Free Tibet班人唔同支那人和平友好：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/danieldumbrill/status/1297522920260952065?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdanieldumbrill%2Fstatus%2F1297522920260952065%3Fs%3D21&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97ZvpkyrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=42a86b8f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdanieldumbrill%2Fstatus%2F1297522920260952065%3Fs%3D21&h=5216654a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/danieldumbrill/status/1297522920260952065?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n同支那官方批准嘅「活佛」交換WeChat（暗示西藏信仰幾咁自由）<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/danieldumbrill/status/1297827249295511555?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdanieldumbrill%2Fstatus%2F1297827249295511555%3Fs%3D21&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97ZvpkyrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=1b8e2e28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdanieldumbrill%2Fstatus%2F1297827249295511555%3Fs%3D21&h=a9d18533\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/danieldumbrill/status/1297827249295511555?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n因為清帝國負擔咗Tibet嘅賠款，所以Tibet自古以來屬於China<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲邏輯混亂到呢<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/danieldumbrill/status/1298099966934564866?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdanieldumbrill%2Fstatus%2F1298099966934564866%3Fs%3D21&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97ZvpkyrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=c1248e37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdanieldumbrill%2Fstatus%2F1298099966934564866%3Fs%3D21&h=ad0cbd9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/danieldumbrill/status/1298099966934564866?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n佢個narrative即係：Tibet農奴制下好慘，好似班黑奴咁，而家俾共產黨解放咗，而Dalai 班流亡藏人就好似啲奴隸主一樣想繼續奴役藏人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nso pissed off"},{"pid":"b657a3b77846bf6993cea69c12936dc10a14d113","tid":2176562,"uid":292987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T07:27:57.000Z","msg":"Twitter手足幫手入去屌柒佢好嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c52d2c58f6a00fd921e95240ed4d6b52d910c8c","tid":2176562,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T07:28:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"07f220391b2f7e528b6161feea9a04dc7d679194","tid":2176562,"uid":292987,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T07:28:26.000Z","msg":"貼藏人自焚新聞喺佢tweet下面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe0f2dc76ec1332274da89971af9e9f91bcb383","tid":2176562,"uid":144626,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T07:29:05.000Z","msg":"俾得鬼佬入去, 都只會見到最好<br />\n以前陳日君講過, 佢地冇可能見到地下主教<br />\n只會見到愛國會安排d人, 完全冇代表性"},{"pid":"66709b43ced8e8ca2476a6afb6fcedf343ce9641","tid":2176562,"uid":104106,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T07:29:54.000Z","msg":"依條友唔係左膠<br />\n係tankie嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ccdc23c1170d42448b8948ef5ee4b5f191cfe02","tid":2176562,"uid":292987,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T07:30:23.000Z","msg":"支那